description: Cajun Spechtacular Creations is cookin' up craveable authentic cajun cuisine, and it's no wonder this big ole truck is the newest sensation in the Austin foodie scene.Their menu features all sorts of mouthwatering fixins'; Alligator, Shrimp, and Fish all fried to fresh hot and crunchy perfection. The Crawfish Boil is local legend and their Shrimp & Crawfish etouffee is what we all wish we were eatin’ every day. You’ll also find Cajun Smoked Ribs, Jalapeno Hushpuppies, Seafood Gumbo, and so much mo’. So come on out for some Spechtacular Creations, or have them come cater your next special occasion.
name: Cajun Spechtakular Creations
